---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Figurine Painting Workshop"
  description="Paint decorative ceramic figurines in our pottery painting workshop in Centerville, TN."
  price="$10-15"
  duration="1-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="figurine painting, pottery figurines, ceramic painting, decorative figurines, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Figurine Painting Workshop - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>Bring ceramic figurines to life with color and creativity in our Figurine Painting Workshop at Made @ The Local Pottery and Candle Studio. Paint beautiful decorative figurines that make wonderful gifts or collectibles.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Select from our collection of ceramic figurines—animals, people, mythical creatures, seasonal characters, and more. Using professional-grade paints, you'll paint intricate details, create realistic features, or add imaginative artistic touches. This is detail-focused painting that's both challenging and rewarding. Our experienced instructors guide you through shading, highlighting, and realistic painting techniques. The result is a professional-looking decorative piece you created yourself, perfect for display, collecting, or gift-giving.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Selection of ceramic figurines to paint</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints</li>
      <li>Fine brushes for detail work</li>
      <li>Expert instruction on figurine painting</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Take home your finished figurine</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Collectors wanting custom pieces</li>
      <li>Creating unique decorative gifts</li>
      <li>Detail-oriented artists</li>
      <li>Building display collections</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Select your figurine (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Receive instruction on figurine painting (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint your figurine with guidance (60-90 minutes)</li>
      <li>Final details and touches (10 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $10-15<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Paint your ceramic figurines!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Love painting figurines! This workshop taught me techniques I never knew. My pieces look so detailed and professional!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Carol R.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Been collecting figurines for years. Now I'm painting my own! So satisfying to create something beautiful!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Robert T.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The instructor was so patient with details. My figurine looks like a real artist made it. Highly recommend!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Dorothy W.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Ceramic Painting Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional ceramic painting techniques in our structured workshop.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/ceramic-painting-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Holiday Ornament Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Create custom holiday ornaments for your tree.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/holiday-ornament-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint Your Own Pottery Session</h3>
        <p>Choose from pre-made pottery pieces and paint them your way.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/paint-your-own-pottery-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
